quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,1,"By the [winds] scattering [dust], dispersing [it]"
  51,2,"And the [clouds] carrying a load [of water]"
  51,3,"And the ships sailing with ease"
  51,4,"And the [angels] apportioning [each] matter,"
  51,5,"Indeed, what you are promised is true."
  51,6,"And indeed, the recompense is to occur."